		<title>英·日 중앙은행 운명의 갈림길 속에서 급등英·日 중앙은행 운명의 갈림길 속에서 급등하는 GBP/JPY 환율하는 GBP/JPY 환율</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/gbpjpy-surges-central-banks-determine-fate</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 09:14:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[마켓 뉴스 및 자료]]></category>
